List available bluetooth adapters:confopts_ph.sh -p allowed -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_BLUE | more
List available controller types:confopts_ph.sh -p allowed -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_TYPE | more
List available controller mappings:confopts_ph.sh -p allowed -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_MAP | more
Show selected bluetooth adapter:confopts_ph.sh -p get -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_BLUE | more
Show selected controller type:confopts_ph.sh -p get -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_TYPE | more
Show selected controller mapping:confopts_ph.sh -p get -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_MAP | more
Select bluetooth adapter (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_BLUE -s
Select bluetooth adapter (Method='NoExpand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_BLUE -s -r
Select controller type (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_TYPE -s
Select controller type (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_TYPE -s -r
Select controller mapping (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_MAP -s
Select controller mapping (Method='NoExpand'):confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers -o PH_CTRL_MAP -s -r
Select all options (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -s
Select all options (Method='NoExpand'):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -s -r
Reset all options:confopts_ph.sh -a Controllers -p reset | more
List all options:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Controllers | more
Display option help (Method='NoExpand'):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -d
Display option help (Method='Expand'):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -d -r
Go to Controllers:ph_show_menu Controllers
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
